com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface AIXLocalService

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
AIXLocalServiceImpl
public interface AIXLocalService
extends com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability

A representation of the model object 'AIX Local Service'.

The following features are supported:

  • Action Type
  • Executable Path
  • Service Description
  • Startup Run Level Eight
  • Startup Run Level Five
  • Startup Run Level Four
  • Startup Run Level Nine
  • Startup Run Level One
  • Startup Run Level Seven
  • Startup Run Level Six
  • Startup Run Level Three
  • Startup Run Level Two
  • Startup Run Level Zero

See Also:
OsPackage.getAIXLocalService()
